      "prompt": "Create a temp project directory containing the file src/app/guards/auth.guard.ts. Run scripts/map-ticket-relationships.py with ticket_key OC-4644, codebase_root set to the temp project directory, infer_by_file true, and ticket_data containing related_tickets with parent OC-4000 and linked [OC-4500] and a description that mentions src/app/guards/auth.guard.ts. Verify the relationship graph contains the parent, the linked ticket, and the affected file.",
